{
  "lyrics": [
    {
      "start": 0,
      "end": 26.400000000000002,
      "text": "Paint yourself a picture of what you wish you looked like."
    },
    {
      "start": 26.4,
      "end": 32.199999999999996,
      "text": "Maybe then they just might feel an ounce of your pain."
    },
    {
      "start": 32.199999999999996,
      "end": 37.4,
      "text": "Come into focus, step out of the shadows."
    },
    {
      "start": 37.4,
      "end": 40.48,
      "text": "It\u0027s a losing battle."
    },
    {
      "start": 40.48,
      "end": 47.959999999999994,
      "text": "There\u0027s no need to be ashamed."
    },
    {
      "start": 47.959999999999994,
      "end": 51.239999999999995,
      "text": "Because they don\u0027t even know you."
    },
    {
      "start": 51.239999999999995,
      "end": 53.96,
      "text": "All they see is scars."
    },
    {
      "start": 53.96,
      "end": 59.36,
      "text": "They don\u0027t see the angel living in your heart."
    },
    {
      "start": 59.36,
      "end": 64.8,
      "text": "Let them find the real you buried deep within."
    },
    {
      "start": 64.8,
      "end": 74.24000000000001,
      "text": "And let them know with all you\u0027ve got that you are not your skin."
    },
    {
      "start": 74.24000000000001,
      "end": 81.24000000000001,
      "text": "Oh, oh."
    },
    {
      "start": 81.24,
      "end": 87,
      "text": "Now when they start to judge you, show them your true colors."
    },
    {
      "start": 87,
      "end": 92.83999999999999,
      "text": "And do unto others as you\u0027d have done to you."
    },
    {
      "start": 92.83999999999999,
      "end": 95.24,
      "text": "Just rise above this."
    },
    {
      "start": 95.24,
      "end": 98,
      "text": "Kill them with your kindness."
    },
    {
      "start": 98,
      "end": 101.03999999999999,
      "text": "Ignorance is blindness."
    },
    {
